- there are a lot of `...Schema.ts` files in the project, follow the pattern of these files
- `...Schema.ts` files should contain 3 exports:
- an exported interface (`Todo`)
- an exported schema (e.g. `todoSchema`)
- an exported validator type (e.g. `export const validate: TypesAreEqual<Todo, TypeOf<typeof todoSchema>> = 'same'`)
- the interface should never use `typeof` of a locally defined schema, it should always duplicate the typescript types

